snippet.title: Alone - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
#indiegame #gametrailers #trailer #steam 

Alone is nearing its launch on Steam!

Wishlist Alone now!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1686490/Alone/

Follow development on Twitter!

https://twitter.com/AloneGame7

Alone is a 2D puzzle-platformer where you control more than one character! Waking up in a mysterious place, with no trace of your memories, you realize you are not alone...

Trailer Music by: Steven O'Brien
https://www.steven-obrien.net/

- Stay Positive (Steven O'Brien)
